==Описание==

The {{Button|[[File:Spreadsheet_SplitCell.svg|16px]] [[Spreadsheet_SplitCell|Spreadsheet SplitCell]]}} tool splits apart a cell that was merged into one in an existing spreadsheet in the active document.

==Применение==

# Make sure there is an active {{Button|[[File:Spreadsheet_CreateSheet.svg|16px]] [[Spreadsheet_CreateSheet|Spreadsheet]]}} open so that the button is enabled.
# Select a cell that was previously {{Button|[[File:Spreadsheet_MergeCells.svg|16px]] [[Spreadsheet_MergeCells|Merged]]}}.
# Press the {{Button|[[File:Spreadsheet_SplitCell.svg|16px]] [[Spreadsheet_SplitCell|Spreadsheet SplitCell]]}} button.


